        <mxCell id="Ji4N8XcLmkFzxe6w8_ma-10" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=28;fontStyle=1" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;1. Validate the user token to ensure the authentication and authorization.&lt;br&gt;2. Verify SMO Connectivity&lt;br&gt;3. Get NearRTRICID and NodeType from Database&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;4. Build Configuration Request Body.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;5. Send Request &amp;amp; Validate Response.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;POST&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font&gt;/nbiapi/get-config/{gnbID}&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Host: &amp;lt;SMOHOST&amp;gt;:&amp;lt;SMOPORT&amp;gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0)); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;Payload:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; padding: 0px; line-height: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;{&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;node&quot;: [&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;{&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;nodeId&quot;: &quot;&amp;lt;NodeID&amp;gt;&quot;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;input&quot;:&amp;nbsp; {&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;managedElement&quot;: {&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&quot;id&quot;: &quot;1&quot;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(0, 0, 0));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;}&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; ]&lt;br&gt;}&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
